default1.4
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe housing costs component of Universal Credit (UC) will not constitute a “clean sheet
default”. The essential structure of HB (and support for mortgage interest) will carry through into UC
default, along with a 
defaultnumber of associated problems
default, which we explore below
default.
