defaultHelp with mortgage costsdefault&#xa0;default2.11
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultA very limited 
defaultSupport for Mortgage Interest 
default(SMI) 
defaultscheme helps with mortgage interest for people receiving out-of-work 
defaultmeans-tested 
defaultbenefits. It is 
defaultrestricted by waiting periods, time limits for certain groups and 
