default2.27
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThis issue reflects a wider problem. 
defaultAlthough people on low incomes often – of necessity – have excellent financial survival skills, claimants face new challenges relating to benefit cuts and payment changes.
default 
defaultAs part of our Managing Migration project, w
defaulte r
defaultecently surveyed
default over 1,700
default of our
default clients who will start to receive 
defaultUC
default from October
